casebody.data:
Vamsidhar VURIMINDI, petitioner,
v.
The HOOPSKIRT LOFTS CONDOMINIUM ASSOCIATION. No. 18-5881. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 5, 2018.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Commonwealth Court of Pennsylvania dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
